BLUES BROTHERS, THE:

        On the character select screen, type "WALLOO" (the background will
        change to maroon).  Press a number ('1'-'6') then the 'SPACEBAR' to
        go to the corresponding level.

        On the character select screen, type "HOULQ" (the background will
        change to maroon).  Press a number ('1'-'6') then the 'SPACEBAR' to
        go to the corresponding level.

        When finishing a level, get the second of the two flags, and you'll
        keep your record collection through to the next level.
